OL,6,FRed, White and Blue depicts a reality
OL,7,Ffor American women who, desperate for
OL,8,Fan abortion, are sometimes forced to
OL,9,Fcross borders to find a state where
OL,10,Fthe procedure is still legal.
OL,12,FThe film was produced in response to
OL,13,Fthe in 2022, which had, since the
OL,14,F1970s, guaranteed women's right to a
OL,15,Fsafe abortion.
OL,17,FIt brought protestors onto the streets
OL,18,Fin America and prompted British
OL,19,Fscreenwriter Nazrin Choudhury, who
OL,20,Flives in the US, to create Red, White
OL,21,Fand Blue.
