OL,6,FFirst-time director Ms Choudhury said
OL,7,Fthat the film's Oscar nomination is
OL,8,Fimportant with the US Presidential
OL,9,FElection fast approaching.
OL,11,F"We are talking about abortion and
OL,12,Freproductive rights, and so it's
OL,13,Fgratifying for our film, it's
OL,14,Fgratifying for our cast and crew, but
OL,15,Fmost importantly to represent the
OL,16,Fpeople whose voices can't be seen or
OL,17,Fheard ordinarily, who need this kind
OL,18,Fof healthcare," she said.
OL,20,F"We're just grateful that it puts the
OL,21,Fspotlight on that and on them."
